dback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 16, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104xgp1665702680386.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/xgp1665702680386.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/xgp1665702680386.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"xgp1665702680386\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Specify the text of the message body.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"xgp1665702680386__topic_d134579e1_d134580e1_d134581e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xgp1665702680386__p_d134582e1_d134583e1_d134584e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">SetMessage</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">(</code><var class=\"keyword varname\">Message</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">\"</code>{<var class=\"keyword varname\">OptionList</var>}<code class=\"ph codeph\">\")</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"xgp1665702680386__section_ulg_hth_fwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d458571e73\">Parameters</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"4\" id=\"xgp1665702680386__table_w4355ab1b5b3b3_w4356ab1b5b3_w4357ab1b5_w4358ab1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"xgp1665702680386__table_w4355ab1b5b3b3_w4356ab1b5b3_w4357ab1b5_w4358ab1__entry__1\">Parameter</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"xgp1665702680386__table_w4355ab1b5b3b3_w4356ab1b5b3_w4357ab1b5_w4358ab1__entry__2\">Type</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"xgp1665702680386__table_w4355ab1b5b3b3_w4356ab1b5b3_w4357ab1b5_w4358ab1__entry__3\">Direction</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"xgp1665702680386__table_w4355ab1b5b3b3_w4356ab1b5b3_w4357ab1b5_w4358ab1__entry__4\">Description</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xgp1665702680386__table_w4355ab1b5b3b3_w4356ab1b5b3_w4357ab1b5_w4358ab1__entry__1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Message</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xgp1665702680386__table_w4355ab1b5b3b3_w4356ab1b5b3_w4357ab1b5_w4358ab1__entry__2\">string</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xgp1665702680386__table_w4355ab1b5b3b3_w4356ab1b5b3_w4357ab1b5_w4358ab1__entry__3\">In</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xgp1665702680386__table_w4355ab1b5b3b3_w4356ab1b5b3_w4357ab1b5_w4358ab1__entry__4\">Text of the message; maximum of 10240000 bytes. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xgp1665702680386__table_w4355ab1b5b3b3_w4356ab1b5b3_w4357ab1b5_w4358ab1__entry__1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">OptionList</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xgp1665702680386__table_w4355ab1b5b3b3_w4356ab1b5b3_w4357ab1b5_w4358ab1__entry__2\">string</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xgp1665702680386__table_w4355ab1b5b3b3_w4356ab1b5b3_w4357ab1b5_w4358ab1__entry__3\">In</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xgp1665702680386__table_w4355ab1b5b3b3_w4356ab1b5b3_w4357ab1b5_w4358ab1__entry__4\">Associative list of key-value pairs, to a maximum of\n          10240 bytes. Currently, the only valid key is <code class=\"ph codeph\">MIMEType</code>, which can\n          be set to <code class=\"ph codeph\">text/HTML</code> or <code class=\"ph codeph\">text/plain</code>. <p class=\"p\">If omitted,\n              <code class=\"ph codeph\">MIMEType=\"text/plain\"</code> is used.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"xgp1665702680386__section_vcs_3th_fwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d458571e166\">Return Values</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"xgp1665702680386__table_d16103e1_d16104e1_d16105e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Values returned in $status</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"xgp1665702680386__table_d16103e1_d16104e1_d16105e1__entry__1\">Value</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"xgp1665702680386__table_d16103e1_d16104e1_d16105e1__entry__2\">Description</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xgp1665702680386__table_d16103e1_d16104e1_d16105e1__entry__1\">0</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xgp1665702680386__table_d16103e1_d16104e1_d16105e1__entry__2\">Operation succeeded</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xgp1665702680386__table_d16103e1_d16104e1_d16105e1__entry__1\">-18</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xgp1665702680386__table_d16103e1_d16104e1_d16105e1__entry__2\">Memory allocation error</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xgp1665702680386__table_d16103e1_d16104e1_d16105e1__entry__1\">&lt;0</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xgp1665702680386__table_d16103e1_d16104e1_d16105e1__entry__2\">An error occurred</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"xgp1665702680386__section_af5_jth_fwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d458571e227\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">Use the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">SetMessage</span> operation to specify the message content and its MIME\n        type.</p>\n<p class=\"p\">To specify a multi-part message with both MIME types, use <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">SetMessage</span>\n        twice. For example, the following code uses the contents of both the TEXT and the HTML\n        fields to constructs a multi-part message:</p>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104xgp1665702680386_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"xgp1665702680386__codeblock_hv1_5th_fwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">mailApiHandle-&gt;SetMessage(TEXT.MESSAGE, \"\") ; plain text body\nmailApiHandle-&gt;SetMessage(HTML.MESSAGE, \"MIMEType=text/html\") ; HTML body</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\">If you set the different text but the same MIMEType, the earlier text will be replaced by\n        the later text. For example, the following code use uses the contents of the HTML field\n        only, because the MIME type for both messages is the same:</p>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104xgp1665702680386_html_1\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"xgp1665702680386__codeblock_xwy_5th_fwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">mailApiHandle-&gt;SetMessage(TEXT.MESSAGE, \"MIMEType=text/plain\") \nmailApiHandle-&gt;SetMessage(HTML.MESSAGE, \"MIMEType=text/plain\")</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"xgp1665702680386__section_pp4_rn3_bdc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d458571e255\">Example: Using SetMessage</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">The following example specifies an HTML message using the contents of the field BODY_HTML\n        as the message text.</p>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104xgp1665702680386_html_2\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"xgp1665702680386__codeblock_rk3_wth_fwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">variables\n handle mailApiHandle\nendvariables\n\n; create the instance handle\nnewinstance \"UPOPMAIL\", mailApiHandle\n\n&lt;snip&gt;log on to server, set message header &lt;/snip&gt;\n\n; set the message body\nmailApiHandle-&gt;SetMessage(BODY_HTML.MESSAGE.DUMMY, \"MIMEType=text/html\") ; HTML body\n...\n&lt;snip&gt; send mail, clear memory, and log off mail server&lt;/snip&gt;</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2533717\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2533717\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "SetMessage Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 16, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Specify the text of the message body. SetMessage ( Message \" { OptionList } \") Parameters Parameter Type Direction Description Message string In Text of the message; maximum of 10240000 bytes. OptionList string In Associative list of key-value pairs, to a maximum of 10240 bytes. Currently, the only valid key is MIMEType , which can be set to text/HTML or text/plain . If omitted, MIMEType=\"text/plain\" is used. Return Values Table 1. Values returned in $status Value Description 0 Operation succeeded -18 Memory allocation error <0 An error occurred Description Use the SetMessage operation to specify the message content and its MIME type. To specify a multi-part message with both MIME types, use SetMessage twice. For example, the following code uses the contents of both the TEXT and the HTML fields to constructs a multi-part message: Explain this code mailApiHandle->SetMessage(TEXT.MESSAGE, \"\") ; plain text body mailApiHandle->SetMessage(HTML.MESSAGE, \"MIMEType=text/html\") ; HTML body Copy If you set the different text but the same MIMEType, the earlier text will be replaced by the later text. For example, the following code use uses the contents of the HTML field only, because the MIME type for both messages is the same: Explain this code mailApiHandle->SetMessage(TEXT.MESSAGE, \"MIMEType=text/plain\") mailApiHandle->SetMessage(HTML.MESSAGE, \"MIMEType=text/plain\") Copy Example: Using SetMessage The following example specifies an HTML message using the contents of the field BODY_HTML as the message text. Explain this code variables handle mailApiHandle endvariables ; create the instance handle newinstance \"UPOPMAIL\", mailApiHandle <snip>log on to server, set message header </snip> ; set the message body mailApiHandle->SetMessage(BODY_HTML.MESSAGE.DUMMY, \"MIMEType=text/html\") ; HTML body ... <snip> send mail, clear memory, and log off mail server</snip> Copy Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}